text: St. Jorgen's Day () is a 1930 Soviet silent comedy movie directed by Yakov Protazanov.Недосягаемый, неисчерпаемыйПраздник святого Йоргена It stars Igor Ilyinsky, Anatoly Ktorov, and Mikhail Klimov. ==Actors== * Igor Ilyinsky as Franz Schulz * Anatoly Ktorov as Michael Korkis * Mikhail Klimov as adjunct of the St. Jorgen church * Ivan Arkadin as treasurer of St. Jorgen Church * Mariya Strelkova as Oleandra == References == ==Other websites== * Category:Soviet silent movies Category:1930 movies Category:Soviet comedy movies
title: St. Jorgen's Day
